,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢樣真係遠離中國<br />\n中國一定係最慢果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣要發展 d人最好同大陸文化差異大<br />\n思想越進步就越唔會同d野人相處到</blockquote><br />\n未必<br />\n支那只係利益行頭<br />\n如果同性戀對啲貪官有利，可以消費嘅話<br />\n共產黨未必最慢<br />\n日本會係文化方面鞏固，可能都會幾慢都未頂<br />\n《日本國憲法》第24條規定：「婚姻僅以兩性的自願結合為基礎而成立<br />\n憲法都寫明要兩性，連JD都冇得搞<br />\n而且日本不嬲都係老人政治、老人頑固唔畀同性戀嘅話，後生開明都冇用。而日本人正正係古板"},{"pid":"7f388739287297c3d34519c60285f5729b35194b","tid":257072,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"d gay佬去晒台灣就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc7579c25ca1f59724d8867761ac59fe8f400ca","tid":257072,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d gay佬去晒台灣就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLesbian呢咁？"},{"pid":"c8cf75bb0604dc4c48b163d91b9a46d81eb6e23d","tid":257072,"uid":99225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"中國性方其實仲開放過日本香港"},{"pid":"6c607735f7c29d25d0e75a37c7f4ff89109b69a3","tid":257072,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國性方其實仲開放過日本香港</blockquote><br />\n開放過香港冇問題<br />\n問放過日本你都講得出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n性開放程度唔止得異性走向同性一個方向可以比較囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b1cc3991ba66b25eee27c062207acb10fcc813","tid":257072,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國性方其實仲開放過日本香港</blockquote><br />\n開放過香港冇問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">開</span>放過日本你都講得出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n性開放程度唔止得異性走向同